{"tid":1692983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[係咪想TVB死]唔洗入電視城！開始召集TVB 和你塞！","createTime":"2019-11-04T10:57:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-05T04:53:11.000Z","uid":1670,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"1a30380e1447a8dc23510bf8ce813a47c2d6fb77","tid":1692983,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:57:12.000Z","msg":"入黎話你聽要搞tvb根本唔洗入電視城，難入難出就係我地嘅優勢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691486\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691486</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n經過上post討論，相信呢個方法都有一定程度可行<br />\n所以要搞TVB嘅，唔洗入電視城，直攻628<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>實際日子係幾多？</ins><br />\n因為上個post有巴打講過，如果係事前知道，tvb係有back up plan,所以我建議tvb和你塞係以快閃形式，返工時段開始聚人，口罩為記號，齊人就開始。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>628係城巴，會唔會得罪咗城巴個邊？</ins><br />\n<br />\n行動可以係唔傷及城巴之下進行，阻塞車程，車上貼連儂牆等等都係可行<br />\n<br />\n<ins>tvb記者都唔會返電視城？搞黎做乜？</ins><br />\n<br />\n記住我地唔係單純針對tvb新聞，只有針對成個tvb,影響佢嘅製作，影響佢嘅運作先可以達至攬炒<br />\n<br />\n<ins>有啲員工唔係靠628返工，點搞？</ins><br />\n<br />\n有巴打提及有員工係靠其他巴士返工，但其實只有628係可以確保全部都係tvb人。以唔影響其他人為設想，搞628係首要選項<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多細節可以再傾，可行嘅就應該去做<br />\n歡迎再多現任或前任tvb員工爆料<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daccb6130897174ea756a0ad187ca791213cba8a","tid":1692983,"uid":109820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T10:58:44.000Z","msg":"推 順便借位<br />\n<br />\n【認真參考日本社運】想行得遠過藍絲，不如唔好再鬧同路人啲ig？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1692734\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1692734</a>"},{"pid":"58e3a167c64a7be7b346c3f484d8ee355b45cbef","tid":1692983,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:03:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8adeb603aecaf3f3751aa66945161bfe3db544c9","tid":1692983,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:08:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d485423f6d75c501add738f19644b698241d3e31","tid":1692983,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad26f40a5abaf3da09acdcb3c115386b0a99ceab","tid":1692983,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:31:13.000Z","msg":"警甴"},{"pid":"6d1d522d7b132742777c4d593d35615089dc0d54","tid":1692983,"uid":1670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h0OntRy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh0OntRy.png&h=c09293e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\